            , saw in the kitchen when the prisoner was below: the prisoner sent up the maid for a broom, and followed her, and flung down the basket of dust, and made off; the spoons were never found: the prisoner was taken next day.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. The cart went on, and the horse's shoe came off, or else I should have come back.</p>
               <p>King. He said before the Justice, he had not been dusting for five days.</p>
